title: Is The 2015 Camaro Z28 Worth $75,000? -- AFTER/DRIVE
description: No other Camaro in history has ever been as ready to take to the track right from the dealership as the 2015 Camaro Z/28. But is it worth your $75,000? With Jason Harper, Bloomberg News and Automobile, and Travis Okulski, Jalopnik.
